          "description": "I can\u2019t recommend this place enough. I came in after being sick for weeks and they saw me promptly and gave me a call to follow up a few days later to check in and see how I was doing. When I needed another medication a week later I called and they connected me with the doctor, who quickly prescribed it to me on the spot. Excellent service and convenient location",
