          "description": "Booked an appointment and was seen within 20 minutes of checking in! The doctor gave me a quick diagnosis and prescribed me the meds I needed. I will absolutely come back here any time I need urgent care in the future. The receptionist was also very friendly and helped walk me through the online check in process.",
