          "description": "I went in for an earache, and the Optum doctor couldn\u2019t find anything, but two days later I went to my regular doctor who found that I had a sinus infection and prescribed me steroids and antibiotics. Too bad this was missed as I suffered for two extra days and the visit accomplished nothing.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GYVdVZ3lUbHB5VWxKMVJFUjZkSFZLWDFwV1RVRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x6c517ccf47fc5af2!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOnFaWUgyTlpyUlJ1RER6dHVKX1pWTUE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "3 months ago",
