          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-CRhnaK7aQszBAnQSu-k2O82piNf0RAjMP0HAfRa4Ia_2acqc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I made an appointment for 8:45 and arrived 10 minutes early only to not be called for over an hour and a half. After being called back I then had to wait another almost hour to be seen by the doctor. This is absolutely ridiculous and outrageous that with an appointment the wait time is over 2 hours long. There was people who got there after me and were walk in seen and left before me. All because the lady at the front desk \u201cforgot about me\u201d. This has been the worst experience I\u2019ve ever had going to a CityMD and I will never be back. The staff as no sense of urgency or respect for peoples time. Don\u2019t go here if you are looking for a fast and friendly experience.\n\nWorst place ever!!",
